case.title: Do you think you have a nice voice? Call me, let's talk. - 33 (NY)
case.text: Females only, imagine how much more you can say to a person in ten minutes instead of 100 emails going back and forth. My description is 5'9, black hair, brown eyes, slim and White. Any race is fine but please be slim and 35 and under. (seven 1 8) three 5 four, 83 66
